1.title: Stuck at Christmas
1.plot: Harley rallies her siblings and parents to take a trip to Florida to celebrate Christmas with their grandma, but in true Diaz fashion, things go awry.

2.title: Stuck with Rachel's Secret
2.plot: When Rachel apparently misses out on an incredible educational opportunity, her sisters are suspicious of how well she takes the news. Meanwhile, Ethan cashes in on his experience of living with four sisters by landing a job.

3.title: Stuck with a Diaz Down
3.plot: As the Diazes cope with their new family dynamics, Ethan reluctantly asks his sisters for advice on girls.

4.title: Stuck In Camp Chaos
4.plot: As Harley tries to raise money, by running a day camp for the neighborhood kids, in the Diaz backyard, she finds herself distracted by the new neighbor, Ellie's irritating cousin, Aiden.

5.title: Stuck with Harley's Bethany
5.plot: Harley and Suzy try a new strategy to get along with their difficult neighbors.

6.title: Stuck in a Nice Relationship
6.plot: Georgie enlists Harley's help to break up with Wyatt.

7.title: Stuck with Horrible Helpers
7.plot: Harley's latest invention causes havoc in science class.

8.title: Stuck in a Mysterious Robbery
8.plot: When the Bait N' Bite is robbed, the Diaz kids use their resources to track down the culprit.

9.title: Stuck in a Besties Battle
9.plot: Under Abuela's watch for the weekend, the Diaz kids are committed to making her visit disaster-free, that is, until Harley learns that Ethan spilled her deepest secret.

10.title: Stuck in Spring Break
10.plot: Spring vacation, here the Diazes come. The Diaz's must deliver a luxury yacht. They live it up until they dock at the port next to the dreaded Pillman family.

11.title: Stuck with a New Squad
11.plot: When Georgie fails to make the basketball team this year, Harley helps her cultivate a new passion instead.

12.title: Stuck with a Non-Diaz
12.plot: Harley goes all out to convince popular neighborhood blogger, Shane Coleman, to feature Ethan's latest film project about Zombies.

13.title: Stuck in the Dark
13.plot: Harley learns that her opportunity to meet one of her scientific heroes depends upon her ability to rein in Daphne. Meanwhile, Ethan faces some hard decisions in forming a band for the Marshport Seafood Festival.

14.title: Stuck with No Escape
14.plot: Harley noticed the Diaz kids aren't as tight-knit lately, so she uses her Lock Squawk invention to turn the attic into an escape room and acts as the game master.

15.title: Stuck Wrestling Feelings
15.plot: Harley realizes that she had a great time hanging out with a surprisingly sweet and generous Aidan, despite a chaotic day. Georgie calls her out for crushing on Aidan.

16.title: Stuck Without the Perfect Gift
16.plot: Aidan gets Harley a special gift.

17.title: Stuck in Diaz Court
17.plot: When the family car rolls into the garage and causes severe damage, Tom and Suzy look for a culprit; Ethan and Harley don't have alibis, so they head to Diaz Court.

18.title: Stuck in Dad's Birthday
18.plot: Harley discovers that the confusing circumstances surrounding the time she was born literally cost her dad the vehicle of his dreams, now more than fifteen years later, she attempts to rectify the situation on his birthday.

19.title: Stuck in a Fake Out
19.plot: Ellie volunteers to be the videographer at Harley's upcoming quinceanera, except she does not have a good track record.

20.title: Stuck in Harley's Quinceañera
20.plot: It's quince day. Harley enlists the help of the Littles to tackle what's left of her Buck-Kid List before she becomes an official adult.

1.title: Pilot
1.plot: Avid inventor Harley is all set to accept a community award, but must first devise a way to get her family out of the house and to the ceremony on time.

2.title: Stuck in the Sweet Seat
2.plot: Harley's parents forget her birthday, so she devises a plan to use their guilt as a way to get the ultimate birthday gift.

3.title: Stuck with a Guy on the Couch
3.plot: To raise money to replace her family's broken tablet, Harley decides to rent out the family's couch to a foreign exchange student.

4.title: Stuck at the Movies
4.plot: When Harley procrastinates on finishing her science project, it inadvertently leads to the WIFI going out, leading her entire family to head out to the movies.

5.title: Stuck in the Block Party
5.plot: Harley decided she's going to create an activity for the annual block party but struggles to find the perfect idea.

6.title: Stuck in the Slushinator
6.plot: Harley uses her creativity to convince her dad to hire her at his marina store. Once there, she unveils her newest invention, the "slushinator."

7.title: Stuck in the Mother's Day Gift
7.plot: Harley decides to go solo on a Mother's Day gift, rather than include the rest of her siblings.

8.title: Stuck in Harley's Comet
8.plot: Harley decides to host an outdoor slumber party so she can watch a passing comet with all of her friends.

9.title: Stuck with Mom's New Friend
9.plot: Harley's dad goes out of town and her mom becomes extremely clingy; she tries to find her mom a new friend.

10.title: Stuck with My Sister's Boyfriend
10.plot: When Rachel's boyfriend Cuff decides to make himself at home in the Diaz house, Harley tries to find a way to get him out!

11.title: Stuck with a Winner
11.plot: With basketball season over, Harley helps Georgie secure a spot on the golf team; mom puts the kids up to a cooking challenge when they complain about her food.

12.title: Stuck with No Rules
12.plot: The parents go away for the weekend, leaving Harley and her siblings to their own devices; Rachel tries to make her friends jealous with Harley's help.

13.title: Stuck in the Harley Car
13.plot: Harley's latest invention is the "HarleyCar," a pedicab that can transport kids all over town. But when Ethan becomes an investor, Harley is forced to share the bike with him.

14.title: Stuck in Lockdown
14.plot: When Harley get put on lockdown, she calls on her BFTF Ethan to help her prove that Daphne isn't as innocent as she seems.

15.title: Stuck Without a Ride
15.plot: Harley needs a ride to Boston for an inventor's contest; her dad is away and her mom is busy with her siblings so she turns to Rachel for a ride.

16.title: Stuck in the Quinceañera
16.plot: The whole family chips in enough money to give Georgie a quinceanera; Lewie and Beast are busy tracking a hurricane.

17.title: Stuck in the Diaz of Our Lives
17.plot: The Diaz family is given the once-in-a-lifetime chance to star in their very own reality television show.

1.title: Stuck in the Waterpark
1.plot: The Diaz family go to a water park

2.title: Stuck in a Commercial
2.plot: Harley and Ethan make a TV commercial for their dad's store.

3.title: Stuck in the School Photo
3.plot: Things go awry for the Diaz kids during school picture day.

4.title: Stuck in a Slushy War
4.plot: A slushy war breaks out when Harley's Slushy Shack faces new competition.

5.title: Stuck in the Garage Sale
5.plot: Hoping for enough money to buy an above-ground pool, the children work together to pull off a garage sale.

6.title: Stuck in the Diaz Easter
6.plot: The Diaz kids team up to save their family holiday traditions from disappearing.

7.title: Stuck in the Beast-day Party
7.plot: After discovering a shocking truth about Beast's birthday, Harley throws him an epic party that causes a rift between the twins.

8.title: Stuck Without Devices
8.plot: The kids must entertain themselves for an entire weekend without using technology or devices.

9.title: Stuck with a Boy Genius
9.plot: Harley, Rachel, Georgie and Ethan attend their school spring formal dance, while Lewie and Beast camp out at home in the backyard.

10.title: Stuck with a Bad Influence
10.plot: Harley tries to save Ellie from being sent away to boarding school.

11.title: Stuck in a Good Deed
11.plot: Harley and Suzy volunteer at a local retirement community.

12.title: Stuck Dancing with My Dad
12.plot: When Harley learns business magnate, Troy Havana, will compete on "Dancing with my Dad," she schemes to have her own dad and Daphne also appear on the program.

13.title: Stuck in a Gold Medal Performance
13.plot: The Diaz family hosts Olympic medalist, Laurie Hernandez, for a dinner that spins out of control.

14.title: Stuck in a New Room
14.plot: When the parents leave it up to the kids to decide who will move into the new bedroom in the attic, the kids compete in a ''Diaz Decathlon.''

15.title: Stuck with a Dangerous House
15.plot: The girls have to share their room with Daphne after her playhouse is thrown away.

16.title: Stuck with a New Friend
16.plot: Harley befriends the new girl in school, but the friendship becomes strained when Ethan befriends her too.

17.title: Stuck in a Merry Scary
17.plot: When Harley comes up with different ways to celebrate the festivities of Halloween, she decides to a plan on pulling a practical joke on Rachel.

18.title: Stuck with a Hook, Line and Sinker
18.plot: When a superstar fisherman shows up at the Bait and Bite looking for a place to stay, Harley decides this is the perfect opportunity to raise money for a dream family vacation.

19.title: Stuck in the Babysitting Nightmare
19.plot: Harley tries to prove her babysitting skills by watching Beast, Louie and Daphne on her own.

20.title: Stuck in the Diaz Awards
20.plot: The Diaz family celebrates the best, worst, funniest and most Diaz-y moments of the past year during the annual family awards night.

imdb.plot outline: The single-camera comedy series follows 14-year-old Harley Diaz as she maneuvers her way through the bustle of being a middle child in a family with six other siblings. The heartfelt and comedic stories of a big family find Harley devising creative ways to cope with - and stand out - in her family's busy suburban Massachusetts household. Her ingenuity often wins the day for the Diaz family, even with many different personalities living under one roof.
